-Oh wow.
Is your nickname Diamond Plate Bob?

00:01:22.651 --> 00:01:24.218
[Bob laughs] No.

00:01:24.285 --> 00:01:26.902
-This is where you're sleeping?
-This is my bedroom.

00:01:26.969 --> 00:01:28.073
This is cedar lined.

00:01:28.140 --> 00:01:30.423
We took cedar
