00:01:30.490 --> 00:01:33.193
Then coffee service. Always coffee service.

00:01:33.260 --> 00:01:34.261
Maps.

00:01:34.328 --> 00:01:35.970
This is my desk, computers.

00:01:36.563 --> 00:01:38.532
The kitchen's outside.

00:01:40.630 --> 00:01:42.573
It's a little tight. Surprisingly.

00:01:42.640 --> 00:01:44.443
It's a 26 year old vehicle.

00:01:44.510 --> 00:01:47.663
And I think it was used
